                <div class="citation-box">
                    <p><strong>Research Question:</strong> What is the current state of genetic diversity monitoring for UK livestock breeds, and where are the critical knowledge gaps?</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Key Focus Areas:</strong></p>
                    <ul class="list-top">
                        <li>Compare census-based vs. DNA-based effective population size (Ne) estimates</li>
                        <li>Identify breeds lacking genetic diversity assessments</li>
                        <li>Evaluate conservation priority gaps</li>
                        <li>Recommend future research directions for rare breed conservation</li>
                    </ul>
