                                Quantitative comparison of Ne estimation methods
                                <div class="step-specs">
                                    <strong>Comparison:</strong> Census-based vs. DNA-based Ne estimates<br>
                                    <strong>Test:</strong> Paired t-test for significant differences<br>
                                    <strong>Matching Strategy:</strong> Same sampling year or closest available<br>
                                    <strong>Sample Size:</strong> 53 paired estimates across breeds
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
