                <div class="analysis-grid">
            <div class="analysis-card why-card">
                        <div class="analysis-title">WHY - Conservation Crisis</div>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <strong>The Problem:</strong> UK rare breeds face genetic erosion with incomplete monitoring.
                            
                            <ul>
                                <li>Many breeds lack genetic diversity assessments</li>
                                <li>Census-based monitoring may mask genetic problems</li>
                                <li>Resource allocation needs better genetic evidence</li>
                                <li><span class="highlight">Missing coverage</span> for entire species (turkey, duck, geese)</li>
                                <li>Historical breeds contain unique adaptive variants</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <strong>Conservation Value:</strong> Local breeds provide climate adaptation, disease resistance, and genetic reservoirs for future challenges.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="analysis-card how-card">
            <div class="analysis-title">HOW - Systematic Review Approach</div>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <strong>Comprehensive Methodology:</strong> Multi-database literature survey with systematic screening.
                            
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Literature Search:</strong> Web of Science with targeted search terms</li>
                                <li><strong>Data Integration:</strong> Combine academic studies with government data</li>
                                <li><strong>Gap Analysis:</strong> Compare RBST watchlist with scientific coverage</li>
                                <li><strong>Method Comparison:</strong> Census vs. molecular approaches</li>
                                <li><strong>Quality Assessment:</strong> Systematic data extraction and validation</li>
                            </ul>
                            
                            <strong>Innovation:</strong> First comprehensive assessment linking conservation priorities with genetic research coverage.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="analysis-card what-card">
