                                Identify breed-unique variants for conservation and utilization
                                <div class="step-specs">
                                    <strong>Target:</strong> High priority rare breeds<br>
                                    <strong>Method:</strong> Low-pass sequencing with imputation<br>
                                    <strong>Goals:</strong> Adaptive variants, breed-specific alleles<br>
                                    <strong>Applications:</strong> Conservation breeding, genome editing
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
